milestones.description: Nathan Astle has become the top scorer for NZ in ODIs with 4756 runs, going past Martin Crowe's 4704
Mark Waugh has broken the record for most ducks (16) in ODIs for AUS, going past McDermott's 15
Nathan Astle has scored 39 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for NZ breaking Martin Crowe's record

stories.title: Bond, Astle wreck Australia's party
stories.summary: Though this may have been Australia's national day, New Zealanders' cricketers were again the ones with cause for celebration as another enchanting victory came their way in the VB Series today
